Usage: swapRegularCellWithAlwaysOnCell [-help] [-cellMapFile <string>]
                                       [-defaultAlwaysOnCell <string>]
                                       [-nets <string>] [-verbose]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-cellMapFile <string>             # file name (string, optional)
-defaultAlwaysOnCell <string>     # ao cell name (string, optional)
-nets <string>                    # list of LP-error nets (string, optional)
-verbose                          # (bool, optional)